  "remarks": "\nShahid Hemmat Industrial Group (SHIG) is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for or facilitating a relevant nuclear activity, namely, the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran. For these reasons, SHIG is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.",
